caller_intent: Sandy is following up on insurance renewals, specifically home insurance with Travelers, and wants to consolidate policies again after a previous attempt in 2030. She seeks advice on bundling options and premium changes.
resolution_steps: Confirmed Sandy's home address and moved-in date to verify policy details.
Discussed renewal amounts for home insurance (Travelers) and noted a $146 annual increase.
Explored bundling options, suggesting keeping home insurance with Travelers and switching auto insurance to Progressive for potential discounts.
Advised Sandy not to make any payments until further contact.
Planned to follow up with additional information on bundling and carrier comparisons.
summary: Sandy discusses her home insurance renewal with Heather, noting a $146 increase with Travelers. Heather explores bundling options, suggests switching auto insurance to Progressive for discounts, and advises against immediate payment. A follow-up is planned to finalize recommendations.
